---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Skipping Mondays">
  <main class="page-main" style="padding-top: 18vh; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title" data-split data-en="Privacy Policy" data-de="Datenschutzerklärung" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--cream);">
      <section style="margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;" data-en="1. General Information" data-de="1. Allgemeine Hinweise">1. General Information</h2>
        <p data-en="We take the protection of your personal data very seriously. We treat your personal data confidentially and in accordance with the statutory data protection regulations and this Privacy Policy."
           data-de="Wir nehmen den Schutz Ihrer persönlichen Daten sehr ernst. Wir behandeln Ihre personenbezogenen Daten vertraulich und entsprechend den gesetzlichen Datenschutzvorschriften sowie dieser Datenschutzerklärung.">
           We take the protection of your personal data very seriously. We treat your personal data confidentially and in accordance with the statutory data protection regulations and this Privacy Policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;" data-en="2. Contact Form & Newsletter" data-de="2. Kontaktformular & Newsletter">2. Contact Form & Newsletter</h2>
        <p data-en="If you send us inquiries via the contact form or subscribe to our newsletter, your details from the inquiry form, including the contact details you provided there, will be stored by us for the purpose of processing the inquiry or sending the newsletter. We use Formspree to process these forms."
           data-de="Wenn Sie uns per Kontaktformular Anfragen zukommen lassen oder unseren Newsletter abonnieren, werden Ihre Angaben aus dem Anfrageformular inklusive der von Ihnen dort angegebenen Kontaktdaten zwecks Bearbeitung der Anfrage oder des Newsletters bei uns gespeichert. Wir nutzen Formspree zur Verarbeitung dieser Formulare.">
           If you send us inquiries via the contact form or subscribe to our newsletter, your details from the inquiry form, including the contact details you provided there, will be stored by us for the purpose of processing the inquiry or sending the newsletter. We use Formspree to process these forms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;" data-en="3. Hosting" data-de="3. Hosting">3. Hosting</h2>
        <p data-en="Our website is hosted on Vercel. The provider is Vercel Inc., 340 S Lemon Ave #4133, Walnut, CA 91789, USA. Vercel collects log files of website visitors, which include IP addresses, browser types, and timestamps."
           data-de="Unsere Website wird bei Vercel gehostet. Anbieter ist die Vercel Inc., 340 S Lemon Ave #4133, Walnut, CA 91789, USA. Vercel erhebt Logfiles der Website-Besucher, welche IP-Adressen, Browsertypen und Zeitstempel beinhalten.">
           Our website is hosted on Vercel. The provider is Vercel Inc., 340 S Lemon Ave #4133, Walnut, CA 91789, USA. Vercel collects log files of website visitors, which include IP addresses, browser types, and timestamps.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
